  "title": "Massage Therapist",
  "description": "<p>Massage Therapist (Full Time)</p><p>· To provide Foot Reflexology and Body Massage.</p><p>· Training will be provided.</p><p>· Work 6 days per week, and on Weekends and Public Holidays. Rest day will be a weekday.</p><p>· Working hours: 10am – 9pm</p><p>· Both Male and Female clients</p><p>· Customer service orientated, sales driven and target oriented person</p><p>· Team player with good communication and interpersonal skill</p><p>· Responsible for the maintenance of cleanliness and neatness of the shop</p><p>· Responsible preparing the necessary treatment products, replenishment of stocks, towels supply, etc.</p><p>· Basic + Commission = $3,500 -$5,500.</p><p><strong>Requirements :</strong></p><p>· No experience required</p><p>· ITEC/ WSQ massage certificate will be preferred.</p><p>· Work 6 days per week, and on Weekends and Public Holidays. Rest day will be a weekday.</p><p>· Working hours: 10am – 9pm</p><p><strong>We provide:</strong></p><p>· Attractive commission package</p><p>· work performance incentive</p><p>· Friendly working environment</p><p>· Advanced training for committed staff after 6 months</p><p>Call / SMS : 92962987 (Massage Therapist)</p>",
